      "date": "2012-10-22 07:03:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(12 inline comments)\n\nSome minor style issues that should be cleaned up.\n\nThat said, while I'm not an expert on this code it seems to me that the doi_id->init() method gets the object passed to it, and saves this object in the do_it->{oie_obj,ozi_obj} field.\n\nWhy is it not sufficient to access this field for DNE?  Having some explanation of this in the commit comment would be useful.",
